<dashboard>
<title>D31 Governance Health</title>
<heading/>
<enableWidgetPrinting>false</enableWidgetPrinting>
<documentation>
<author>admin</author>
<description>Governance and metadata health: coverage %, governed/ungoverned mix, missing attributes. Each panel uses a single metric grain to avoid mixed-unit charts.</description>
<icon/>
</documentation>
